Definition: epilepsy in which the attacks involve loss of consciousness and tonic spasms of the musculature followed by generalized jerking
Synonyms: grand_mal, generalized_epilepsy, epilepsia_major, epilepsy, in, which, the, attacks, involve, loss, of, consciousness, and, tonic, spasms, musculature, followed, by, generalized, jerking
Category: noun.state
